    <section id="id6284176">
      <title>Isotopes</title>
      <para id="id6252313">The naturally abundant isotopes of the alkali metals are listed in <link target-id="id1170896090392"/>. All of the isotopes of francium are radioactive. Lithium-7 and sodium-23 are both useful NMR nucleus having I = <sup>1</sup>/<sub>2</sub>. </para>
